0.title: Database List
0.query: timeseries { count(redis.db_config), value.A = avg(redis.db_config, scalar: true) }, by: { db, db_name, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

1.title: Overall Latency

2.title: Read Latency

3.title: Write Latency

4.title: Other Latency

5.title: Memory Usage
5.query: timeseries { avg(redis.redis_server_used_memory), value.A = avg(redis.redis_server_used_memory, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

6.title: CPU Usage
6.query: timeseries { avg(redis.namedprocess_namegroup_cpu_seconds_total, rate: 1s), value.A = avg(redis.namedprocess_namegroup_cpu_seconds_total, rate: 1s, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { ( matchesValue(mode, "system") OR matchesValue(mode, "user") ) AND isNotNull(db) AND matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

subQueries.filter: (mode = system OR mode = user ) db !=  null db=$Database cluster=$Cluster

7.title: Client Connections

8.title: Overall Ops / Sec

9.title: Read Ops / Sec
9.query: timeseries { sum(redis.endpoint_read_requests, rate: 1s), value.A = avg(redis.endpoint_read_requests, rate: 1s, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

10.title: Write Ops / Sec
10.query: timeseries { sum(redis.endpoint_write_requests, rate: 1s), value.A = avg(redis.endpoint_write_requests, rate: 1s, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

11.title: Other Ops / Sec
11.query: timeseries { sum(redis.endpoint_other_requests, rate: 1s), value.A = avg(redis.endpoint_other_requests, rate: 1s, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

12.title: Egress bytes / sec
12.query: timeseries { sum(redis.endpoint_egress, rate: 1s), value.A = avg(redis.endpoint_egress, rate: 1s, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

13.title: Ingress bytes / sec
13.query: timeseries { sum(redis.endpoint_ingress, rate: 1s), value.A = avg(redis.endpoint_ingress, rate: 1s, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

14.title: Read Misses
14.query: timeseries { avg(redis.redis_server_keyspace_read_misses), value.A = avg(redis.redis_server_keyspace_read_misses, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

15.title: Write Misses
15.query: timeseries { avg(redis.redis_server_keyspace_write_misses, rate: 1s), value.A = avg(redis.redis_server_keyspace_write_misses, rate: 1s, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

16.title: Key Count
16.query: timeseries { avg(redis.redis_server_db0_keys), value.A = avg(redis.redis_server_db0_keys, scalar: true) }, by: { cluster, db }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

17.title: Evicted Keys
17.query: timeseries { avg(redis.redis_server_evicted_keys), value.A = avg(redis.redis_server_evicted_keys, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }

18.title: Expired Keys
18.query: timeseries { avg(redis.redis_server_expired_keys), value.A = avg(redis.redis_server_expired_keys, scalar: true) }, by: { db, cluster }, filter: { matchesValue(db, $Database) AND matchesValue(cluster, $Cluster) }
